Title: The Nox
Plot: Pressed by the government to acquire new technologies, SG-1 is led to a world inhabited by a seemingly primative race. When Apophis arrives, SG-1 ambush him with disasterous consequences.
GuestStars: Armin Shimerman, Ray Xifo, Frida Betrani, Terry David Mulligan, Addison Ridge, Michasa Armstrong, Zoran Vukelic
